trans-unit.source: Application Insights (Preview)
trans-unit.target: Application Insights (Preview)

trans-unit.source: Application Insights is a preview service in Microsoft Azure that helps you understand usage patterns and fix problems in your live applications.
trans-unit.target: Application Insights is a preview service in Microsoft Azure that helps you understand usage patterns and fix problems in your live applications.

trans-unit.source: You can obtain and analyze telemetry from web applications (whether in your own servers or on Azure) and Windows devices.
trans-unit.target: You can obtain and analyze telemetry from web applications (whether in your own servers or on Azure) and Windows devices.

trans-unit.source: Detect, triage and diagnose problems and performance issues.
trans-unit.target: Detect, triage and diagnose problems and performance issues.

trans-unit.source: Availability tests to alert you if your service is not visible on the web, or is responding slowly.
trans-unit.target: Availability tests to alert you if your service is not visible on the web, or is responding slowly.

trans-unit.source: Metrics to help diagnose performance issues, such as request rate, response times, CPU usage, dependency responsiveness.
trans-unit.target: Metrics to help diagnose performance issues, such as request rate, response times, CPU usage, dependency responsiveness.

trans-unit.source: Exception reports and alerts.
trans-unit.target: Exception reports and alerts.

trans-unit.source: Capture log traces from your favorite logging frameworks.
trans-unit.target: Capture log traces from your favorite logging frameworks.

trans-unit.source: Continuously improve your application by understanding what your users do with it.
trans-unit.target: Continuously improve your application by understanding what your users do with it.

trans-unit.source: Page view counts, new and returning users, and other core usage analytics.
trans-unit.target: Page view counts, new and returning users, and other core usage analytics.

trans-unit.source: Track your own events and metrics to discover usage patterns.
trans-unit.target: Track your own events and metrics to discover usage patterns.
